**who —** THE PROPULSION LAB — the lab where exotic energy meets the honest verdict

**what —** The Propulsion & Exotic-Energy Lab — eight toolkits from gravitational lensing to anti-gravity, each playable and each marked with what it actually is, no over-unity sold as truth.

**where —** the bench where the dreams of flight and free power are taken down and tested — gravity, light, resonance, plasma, the vacuum itself  Framework inputs: David's energy/propulsion toolkits; general relativity; resonance & plasma physics; the long history of free-energy claims  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0 · Universe David 0)

**why —** Every dream of exotic energy gets the same treatment: open the toolkit, run it, and read the honest verdict — what is real physics, what is grounded speculation, and what is fluff.

**how —** A lab of energy/propulsion toolkits, each live and each rated by the honest-fluff discipline: real, grounded, speculative, or fluff — labelled, not sold.

**◌ the mythos —** Every dream of exotic energy gets the same treatment: open the toolkit, run it, and read the honest verdict — what is real physics, what is grounded speculation, and what is fluff. No miracle endorsed — the real labelled real, the speculative labelled speculative, the fluff labelled fluff.

**the moniker —** ⟦THE PROPULSION LAB:PRL:8701bb⟧ · spoken *zen-than-rak*

**the seal —** Every dream on this bench is playable and every dream is rated — real physics, grounded speculation, and fluff, each marked for what it is, nothing sold as more.

